{"tid":559280,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【賣畀四叔】海航啟德地160億元售予恒地","createTime":"2018-02-13T04:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-14T07:36:59.000Z","uid":70985,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"2dc8f72fee4350c77fa7fea9ac491f12d3f7bd76","tid":559280,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180213/s00002/7e65e927ddfb235909a692cd3d896165.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180213%2Fs00002%2F7e65e927ddfb235909a692cd3d896165.jpg&h=b2d5909e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海航系旗下香港國際建投（0687）剛剛宣布，公司旗下基金就出售持有啟德6565號（1K區3號）地皮及6562號（1L區3號）地皮的SkyHero及TotalThrive的全部權益簽訂買賣協議，買方為恒地（0012）旗下的Shibo Investment Limited及Easco Investment Limited，作價約159.59億元。<br />\n<br />\n海航集團於2016年底起約一個季度內，接連出手，共斥資272億奪得四幅啟德地皮。而6565號地皮為集團於2016年11月投得，成交價88.37億元；6562號地皮於同年12月投得，成交價54.12億元，因此今次帳面計，海航獲利17.1億元<br />\n<br />\n不過，過去一段日子盛傳海航財困，影響到啟德地皮的融資，部份過橋貸款不獲銀行續貸，需要尋求買家接盤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180213/s00002/1518482281617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180213%2Fs00002%2F1518482281617&d=hAob8PXt6f46nKZTGsFS6dtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=c426e8ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180213%2Fs00002%2F1518482281617&h=5f03d872\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180213/s00002/1518482281617</a><br />\n<br />\n四叔接貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c215ecd39c5b8fafbbdff8e513add380e2fdc9d","tid":559280,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T04:59:20.000Z","msg":"焼上身..."},{"pid":"8295aa878c3b4d53eb54236ea3745593f7922af5","tid":559280,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime